{"tid":339282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連仔整個reward scheme 有冇得諗","createTime":"2017-07-29T02:36:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T02:56:33.000Z","uid":11144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3642d873539cd801be61184dd68004e8f8eb1230","tid":339282,"uid":11144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"大家都知道呢個forum既由來<br />\n而呢到最有價值既野係大家既發言、創意<br />\n冇左班會員開高汁po<br />\n個forum一定冇咁多人<br />\n<br />\n而家連登開左差唔多成年<br />\n見連仔都算有心 整下扮工模式咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但始終好似冇左一班高汁會然咁<br />\n如果整個reward scheme<br />\n好似youtube 咁<br />\n按正評黎分豬肉 唔洗好多<br />\n合理既分 而個forum又運作到<br />\n咁可以吸引更多o開po 尤其高汁po<br />\n唔知咁樣有冇得撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbb29f67eae8bb4952ea3ff1c8a9814cf1eacb4","tid":339282,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:56:33.000Z","msg":"刷分呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}